messages.message:
Hi all, I accidentally included config file changes used for local development in with my changes for https://github.com/instabase/instabase/commit/f4a2954d7edf635e8738095bcdd433d8284749ae
(The code was approved but had small PR comments that I addressed, but then accidentally included the aforementioned config file changes).

It doesn't look like it'll cause any problems with any non-local environments, but in case anyone runs into issues between now and tomorrow morning PST when I start work, here's my PR to undo those config file changes. Feel free to approve it and merge it if it will unblock anyone:
https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/48602
